webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) Slightly collorated view towards Nyinkö42 in Lköpping. At the time, Svenska Smöraffaren operated a store in the street. The house beyond is the so-called Borgarhem. Been erected in 1912-13 with Lköpping fabriks and crafts association as a developer - https://www.europeana.eu/item/73/S_OM_photo_OMEA0001240132. Östergötlands museum - http://digitaltmuseum.se/021017433171. Public Domain Mark - http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/
